window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Spinster is as spinster does....</b></p> <p>Georgiana Allen is a spinster, and everybody knows it. She also happens to be one of the writers for the <i>Spinster Chronicles</i>, and everybody knows that, as well. She’s accepted her lot in life, and along with the other spinsters in her circle, takes great pride in the articles she writes and the influence she has. Then, Captain Anthony Sterling infiltrates their group and her life, and Georgie impossibly begins to hope, once more.</p> <p>Tony Sterling had no idea what to expect when he agreed to break up the spinsters for his cousin, but he certainly did not expect Georgie Allen. From the very first meeting, she upends everything he thought a spinster would be, and her beauty and wit keeps him on edge in thrilling ways. The more he gets to know the spinsters, the less he wants to break them up. And the more he wants Georgie in his life. Permanently. </p>"; 
